      why: "Phase-5 workhorse: substitutes any remaining LTyTypeVar in a type with its concrete binding AND mangles generic class/struct names (Dict<string> → Dict_string). This is what makes validate_post_mono pass on rewritten signatures and field types — without it, monomorphized funcs would still expose unbound type vars in their public surface."

